{"type": "article", "id": 15319, "title": "放衣服的包", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-23T06:50:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140803SFKqtEgUBebjVRsl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这款看上去并起眼的皮包是专门装衣物的。它有一个放西装的口袋，卷在最外层，拿出来时不会变皱。中间空出来的地方刚好放鞋，衣服与鞋隔开，不会相互影响。另外，它还有非常丰富的小口袋，使其他物品也能各得其所。如果到了旅馆里，就能直接将包摊平挂起来。这个包是由耐刮的皮革做的，适合出门还有公事要办的人。售价299美元，<a href=\"http://www.jackthreads.com/of-all-threads/bags/duffel/saffiano-weekender-garment-bag/products/155913?vc=3457&amp;utm_source=adaptly&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_campaign=Pinterest_Saffiano&amp;ss1=Pinterest_Saffiano\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142530ky4wJz8hGYBpSfZQ.jpg\" width=\"736\" height=\"2208\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"3.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}